{"tid":1901622,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"畢特：贊奴沙成長遠低於預期 原本能成為巨星的","createTime":"2020-02-28T02:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T02:56:50.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"97c024a6adc7e53b3bafc3c885375d0d789d0afd","tid":1901622,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/02/27/9/9d37920115f18e4a005f69ab3acd7bb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F02%2F27%2F9%2F9d37920115f18e4a005f69ab3acd7bb4.jpg&h=51e10d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《曼徹斯特晚報》報導，曼聯青訓主管畢特近日接受採訪時表示，他認為贊奴沙本該像傑斯一樣，成為一名巨星。<br />\n<br />\n  贊奴沙之前效力曼聯時身披的是傑斯留下的11號波衫，但他的發展並不如預期，經歷了兩次不太成功的租借（多蒙特和新特蘭）後，他最終在2017年夏天980萬英鎊的價格轉投皇家蘇斯達。<br />\n<br />\n  談及贊奴沙，畢特說道：「青訓球員並不是都會成長為巨星或是擁有偉大的職業生涯，但在17、18、19歲的年紀，他們需要得到正確的指導，我覺得贊奴沙原本可以成為一名巨星。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我記得傑斯執教曼聯時，我是他的助教，我們在聯賽中碰上了布魯斯執教的侯城，我們賽前跟布魯斯有過交流，我指向傑斯對布魯斯說：&lsquo;贊奴沙跟他一樣棒。&rsquo;布魯斯說這不可能，但在賽後，布魯斯直接表示，贊奴沙是頂級、頂級的球員。」<br />\n<br />\n  「贊奴沙的成長不如預期是有些令人失望，他現在有了屬於自己的職業生涯，所以有些事情很難講。但我覺得贊奴沙如果有傑斯那樣的心勁的話，他原本能成為一位巨星的。」<br />\n<br />\n  今季至今，贊奴沙為皇家蘇斯達出場19次，攻入5球並有4次助攻入賬。"},{"pid":"4688866756d0e00d0da4ed1075b77ba53a03105d","tid":1901622,"uid":24750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:29:04.000Z","msg":"佢最勁個場 一球左腳一球右腳 救返曼聯"},{"pid":"debb7fd5476a39c31a6bbf81977e3421b87c6793","tid":1901622,"uid":119778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"俾班獌迷害死"},{"pid":"c59853fed66cf045f03564388f97d5b547b11ba1","tid":1901622,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"J仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80fc2a5044a07b30ef19eb1b1934b490c94a4a0","tid":1901622,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:37:11.000Z","msg":"而家先25歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲後生過連仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf042edb6e36c21863b019b291e365a020b1c52b","tid":1901622,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80fc2a5044a07b30ef19eb1b1934b490c94a4a0","tid":1901622,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:37:11.000Z","msg":"而家先25歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲後生過連仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:44:38.000Z","msg":"但係連加特潛力仲高過贊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e750291d17aea615627e2467cd6fa477066e57e","tid":1901622,"uid":128160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:56:50.000Z","msg":"19場5G4A其實都唔係好差啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}